UFC 208 results -- Holm vs. de Randamie: Live blog, updates, fight card, stream Follow along as Holly Holm and Germaine de Randamie battle for the first women's 145-pound title 20m ago â€¢ 1 min read 
Welcome to CBS Sports coverage of UFC 208 where we will see who gets the first women's featherweight title as Holly Holm and Germaine de Randamie battle in Brooklyn. 
Plus, we see if Anderson Silva can get his first win since 2012 when he steps in the cage with Derek Brunson. 
It all gets started at 8 p.m. ET with the prelim fights live on Fox Sports 1 before action switches over to PPV beginning at 10 p.m. ET .
